  <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
    <title>Small Font Mission about small font teams Worldwide</title>
    <meta name="description" content="Understand the small font mission and how small font tooling plus multilingual resources empower product teams worldwide to ship refined typography." />
    <meta name="keywords" content="" />
    <link rel="canonical" href="https://osrsdmmge.online/en/about/" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/assets/site.css" />
    <link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/assets/small-font-icon.svg" />
  </head>
  <body class="bg-midnight text-fog antialiased">
    {{ languageAlert | safe }}
    {{ renderHeader(header) }}
    <main class="mx-auto max-w-4xl px-4 pb-24 pt-12 md:px-8">
      <section class="space-y-8">
        <span class="badge">Our story</span>
        <h1 class="section-title">Small font mission for small font teams</h1>
        <p class="text-secondary">
          Small Font Online helps product teams design crisp, legible microcopy for dense interfaces and constrained displays. The MVP combines a lightweight generator, privacy-first documentation, and multilingual references so teams can audit, iterate, and ship within a single workflow.
        </p>
        <div class="grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-2">
          <article class="panel panel-contrast">
            <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white">Why we exist</h2>
            <p class="mt-3 text-secondary">Microcopy and UI strings often arrive last in the release cycle. We want to flip that process by providing tooling that treats typography, accessibility, and localization as first-class citizens.</p>
          </article>
          <article class="panel panel-contrast">
            <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white">What comes next</h2>
            <p class="mt-3 text-secondary">We are preparing interactive templates, Playwright smoke tests, and usage analytics that respect privacy while surfacing meaningful insights.</p>
          </article>
        </div>
        <aside class="rounded-3xl border border-accent/40 bg-accent/10 p-6 text-fog/80">
          <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white">Roadmap checkpoints</h2>
          <ul class="mt-4 list-disc space-y-2 pl-5">
            <li>Public beta for small font generator presets.</li>
            <li>Component library handoff for design systems.</li>
            <li>Case studies on teams shipping multilingual microcopy.</li>
          </ul>
        </aside>
      </section>
    </main>
    {{ renderFooterSecondary(footer) }}
  </body>
</html>
